title: American Horror Story: Double Feature | Thirst - Season 10 Ep. 3 Preview | FX
author: FX Networks
comment: What's going on in this town?
This season is so good so far. My favorite since a long while.
I was thrilled with the first two episodes.  The cast is stacked and the setting is perfect.  Best two episodes since the early years.
I think the Corona delaying everything actually helped the writers get back to their creative roots because this is the best season I've seen since Freak Show
Culkin is doing a fabulous job on AHS. Glad he is getting a comeback. He deserves the opportunity try to go off the rails with a character. He has the talent to pull it off as well.
description:
